name: Prone back extension
steps: 1. Lie down on your stomach with the arms extended so that they are parallel to the floor, palms down.
2. Slowly lift your arms, upper body and legs from the floor and hold the extension for 3-5 seconds.
3. Return to the starting position and repeat for desired reps.
benifits: Increase your ability to coordinate movement through your lower back.
Leads to better overall back posture.
